WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:07.838
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for joining me today. Praise the Lord. Well, I've seen a lot today.

00:00:07.839 --> 00:00:14.317
Just like I always do, I take communion and I drive around and pray in the spirit.

00:00:14.318 --> 00:00:37.126
I passed the fire station on my right, and as I passed it, I heard '911, 911.'I saw the emergency responders responding to an emergency: major turbulence ahead.

00:00:37.127 --> 00:00:50.146
I looked at the fire station and I thought, 'Lord, what's going on?'All of a sudden, I went into deep groaning and travail in the spirit, praying in the spirit.

00:00:50.147 --> 00:01:06.756
The Lord started to speak to me very strongly. He started showing me a Pearl Harbor event as we see in the days ahead.

00:01:06.757 --> 00:01:20.414
China is becoming desperate, and North Korea is becoming desperate, wanting out from underneath the Western boot.

00:01:20.415 --> 00:01:37.719
I saw North Korea—because they are the social pariah—becoming the person rising up to become the bully. Does that make sense?

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:49.814
It's like the head mafia guy who has his little thugs underneath him that do the bidding for the head mafia leader.

00:01:49.815 --> 00:01:58.319
Like the Godfather, and then the Godfather has henchmen. He has the guys underneath him that carry out the bad things.

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:12.809
China was the Godfather, and North Korea was the hitman. That's what I was seeing; it's the only way I can describe what I saw.

00:02:12.810 --> 00:02:25.276
I saw North Korea being the pawn because of the political side of China having its fingers in all the different countries.

00:02:25.277 --> 00:02:31.074
They didn't want to be looked at as the bad guy for what's about to take place.

00:02:31.075 --> 00:02:36.564
But I kept hearing when I was praying, 'Remember Pearl Harbor.

00:02:36.565 --> 00:02:47.279
Remember Pearl Harbor.'I said, 'Lord, I know that Japan was with Pearl Harbor and all that.'And He said, 'This will be a type and shadow in the days ahead.

00:02:47.280 --> 00:03:03.229
Remember this.'As I was interceding, the Lord was showing me even deeper into the Asian culture as a whole.

00:03:03.230 --> 00:03:13.119
They think differently than the Western culture. Do you know what I'm saying? That's the only way I can describe this to you.

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:19.999
It's kind of like how the African American culture thinks differently than the white American culture. Does that make sense?

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:36.213
Everybody thinks it's just culture, but I saw in this the Asians sticking with their culture, trying to preserve what they believe and their family ties.

00:03:36.214 --> 00:03:47.995
It's a very Asian thing. I saw China being backed into a hole, and I saw a great depression, a financial infrastructure crumbling.

00:03:47.996 --> 00:04:01.373
As this happened, they didn't want to lose their 'Asianness,'their culture, or what they believed in.

00:04:01.374 --> 00:04:09.213
So they were in a place like a samurai warrior ready to turn its sword on itself.

00:04:09.214 --> 00:04:22.774
You want to die with honor; you don't want to die looking disgraceful. That's the way it seemed.

00:04:22.775 --> 00:04:47.158
They were banding together as Asian cultures—North Korea trying to bring in South Korea in these demonic spirits, trying to bring in Vietnam and the Philippines, all coming together to combat the Western culture.

00:04:47.159 --> 00:05:01.269
This was part of the vision that I was seeing. I kept hearing 'Pearl Harbor'echoing in the spirit, a retaliation.

00:05:01.270 --> 00:05:16.976
Then the Lord showed me Canada. I started praying for Canada, and the Lord showed me the scales.

00:05:16.977 --> 00:05:27.823
They have been weighed and found lacking because of the way the people voted. Not all Canadians voted this way.

00:05:27.824 --> 00:05:35.412
Let me say this very clearly: not all Canadians voted this way, but the majority...

00:05:35.413 --> 00:05:52.236
I told you all, the Lord said, 'Pray that it's too big to rig.'But the majority were for going left, into darkness—not conservative, but for darkness.

00:05:52.237 --> 00:06:00.159
Because of this decision, there was a scale that was tipped in the spirit realm.

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:07.827
(That was real thunder as I say this.) Wow, Lord, I hear you. This is so serious.

00:06:07.828 --> 00:06:43.280
I saw the balance of the scales, and because of the decisions that were made to go the ungodly way with sexual perversion, laws, and things that would be put into place, I saw: 'You want this, you can have it.'I saw a new type of STD, a new venereal disease that had never been seen before, which is very gross.

00:06:43.281 --> 00:06:59.877
This is what I saw coming through certain practices. Because I know I have children watching me, I'm trying to be careful how I say this because I have pure ears listening.

00:06:59.878 --> 00:07:16.496
Certain practices are ungodly. Because of these ungodly acts and the reprobate mind wanting to go this way, the scales in the spirit realm were weighed and found lacking.

00:07:16.497 --> 00:07:38.786
This goes for America also. I saw it up by Quebec, and it infiltrated into New York, Boston, and these major cities—a new venereal disease that has never been known before, worse than the AIDS virus.

00:07:38.787 --> 00:07:45.918
Do you understand what I'm trying to say? This is a new virus coming onto the scene.

00:07:45.919 --> 00:08:02.220
I saw judgment begin even in Japan concerning the trafficking coming up from Mexico.

00:08:02.221 --> 00:08:20.084
And I saw, because of touching the children and the young people, this venereal disease will make them eunuchs because of the infection.

00:08:20.085 --> 00:08:29.232
I saw so much infection that they have to do something because there's no cure for it.

00:08:29.233 --> 00:08:44.605
It's a new type of virus, a very serious virus that is transmitted through...

00:08:44.606 --> 00:08:55.437
This is very serious. I saw such a darkness, and the anger of the Lord was so strong.

00:08:55.438 --> 00:09:05.223
I thought I was going to vibrate out of my car as He spoke. The anger was like the thunder above my heavens right now.

00:09:05.224 --> 00:09:18.527
It was that loud, as I hear the rain and the hail. It was very strong—the rebuke and the warning coming from the Father.

00:09:18.528 --> 00:09:39.518
He told me, 'Because of these things that you are seeing, decisions have been made.'Decisions have been made, and you will see a judgment coming on these circumstances because of sexual promiscuity.

00:09:39.519 --> 00:09:47.517
I know I probably butchered it, but I try with my English. This is what I saw.

00:09:47.518 --> 00:09:59.119
Then I saw a mega-earthquake from British Columbia all the way down to San Francisco.

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:14.064
It was an earthquake so massive and devastating on the West Coast that it shook the foundation of the earth.

00:10:14.065 --> 00:10:33.439
I heard the Spirit of the Lord say, 'This earthquake will be so violent and powerful that it will be off all the Richter scales.'A seismic wave will go and be felt clear into Africa and all around the world.

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:41.588
They will feel the seismic earthquake all throughout the countries and all throughout the whole world.

00:10:41.589 --> 00:10:52.683
It will pick up and be so strong that what is about to take place on the West Coast will be felt all throughout the world.

00:10:52.684 --> 00:11:05.323
I saw buildings fall. I saw major skyscrapers falling in British Columbia, all along the seaboard—I saw them fall into the water.

00:11:05.324 --> 00:11:18.759
I saw massive destruction. And I heard the number: 50,000 people will perish from city to city.

00:11:18.760 --> 00:11:26.286
50,000. I saw such a great shaking going through Portland, Oregon and through Seattle.

00:11:26.287 --> 00:11:34.306
I saw that because of the reprobate mind, the cup of sin is full.

00:11:34.307 --> 00:11:45.635
You say, 'Well, what about grace?'But the Lord said, 'Brandon, there is a holding back right now, for the Great Tribulation is trying to kick off.

00:11:45.636 --> 00:11:52.039
Do you understand? But I'm giving one last call to leave the ninety-nine and go after the one.

00:11:52.040 --> 00:12:11.720
And there will be a great harvest of souls, Brandon, for you are My great harvesters.'He saved the best for last, ladies and gentlemen—the ones who are on fire and seeking Him right now.

00:12:11.721 --> 00:12:26.783
I felt the Father's heart concerning this: the concern and the longing for the children He knows are just on the edge of making the best decision they could ever make.

00:12:26.784 --> 00:12:36.267
He is going after them. He knows the hearts that are so hardened they are not ready versus the ones that are just teetering.

00:12:36.268 --> 00:13:03.278
They are right there, and He's just like, "If I could just get one second with them underneath the glory, I know they would change and they wouldn't perish for eternity."I saw the Earth as a whole, and the Lord warned me, "The Great Tribulation is at hand, Brandon.

00:13:03.279 --> 00:13:11.418
This is worse than what anyone in any generation could ever comprehend.

00:13:11.419 --> 00:13:26.803
For this is the cup of wrath, worse than it was on Sodom and Gomorrah, and worse than ancient Rome when it was judged, when all these major civilizations were judged.

00:13:26.804 --> 00:13:36.333
This is worse because the cup of sin is full."He said, "It's not just one nation, Brandon.

00:13:36.334 --> 00:13:46.367
This is a worldwide corruption."It was so dirty when I saw it.

00:13:46.368 --> 00:14:01.025
I could see Jesus's blood on the altar, and the blood was crying out for people to repent and turn from their wicked ways, to humble themselves and repent.

00:14:01.026 --> 00:14:08.638
But many people are still walking in a "soupy grace,"thinking, "I live the way I want to.

00:14:08.639 --> 00:14:15.915
Jesus forgives it all. I'm going to live like a heathen and live like the world because Jesus covers it.

00:14:15.916 --> 00:14:45.277
Once saved, always saved, brother."They want to live like a hellion and believe they're going to make it because they've tried to live a compromising lifestyle, seeking after righteousness and holiness while living in bars and clubs, then saying, "Oh, I repent.

00:14:45.278 --> 00:15:13.927
I don't need to go to church; I am the church. I don't have to support the congregation."I understand if you don't have a church in your local area because of the "knuckleheads"there and you watch on YouTube—I used to have to do that when my daughter was first diagnosed with autism.

00:15:13.928 --> 00:15:21.452
But I'm talking about those who willingly have no excuse and say, "I'd rather go to the beach.

00:15:21.453 --> 00:15:44.683
God isn't convenient for me. Jesus isn't convenient. I like living the way I want to live."Woe unto you for the shaking that's about to take place.

00:15:44.684 --> 00:15:58.985
I saw a great shaking of earthquakes. We are in a time of metamorphosis. A great acceleration is on the land.

00:15:58.986 --> 00:16:13.795
Just as a caterpillar is changed in the cocoon, there will be great change.

