You touched the children, and God's anger is upon this. The decisions made even in Canada—the thunders were rolling above. The Lord told me, "Brandon, this is no more.

00:17:57.683 --> 00:18:24.501
I watch the hearts, and the majority are corrupt before Me."I saw a shaking of the economies and the land with great earthquakes and devastation.

