And going to Japan, which I don't understand. I kept seeing Japan. What is this about Japan? Businessmen. It was disgusting.

00:22:42.123 --> 00:22:57.199
The Lord said, "This will be known as the earthquake heard around the world."I don't know if that's headlines in the newspaper, on the news, or on the internet, but this will be known as the earthquake heard around the world.

